3. **If the user's request involves scheduling, reminders, recurring tasks, pipelines, event triggers, chained prompts, workflows, or any form of deferred/repeated/orchestrated execution, the ONLY valid action is to create/modify clauck jobs in `{JOBS_DIR}/`.**

4. **Two job formats are available — pick the right one:**

